cordings for DIRECTV shows your friends on Facebook & Twitter posted.- Browse the top shows and movies people are currently talking about and set your DVR to record. MORE- Manage your account.- Instant access to Mobile Answer Center link for FAQs.- Browsing functionality is available to everyone.- Recording functionality is available to DIRECTV customers with a DVR only.REQUIREMENTS- Compatible with most Android phones running 2.2 or later.- DIRECTV customers must have a residential home account registered on the DIRECTV website to watch On Demand content and access recording functionality.- Watching On Demand content requires an active Wi-Fi or 3G Internet connection. For best performance, connect to a strong Wi-Fi signal. - Available content is based on your current programming package and premium service. Not all content is available to stream at this time.- Live TV Streaming in-home only channels requires a Wi-Fi connection to your home network and a DIRECTV Plus\xc2\xae HD DVR (models R22, and HR20 or higher) connected to a broadband Internet connection.- Scheduling a recording requires a Wi-Fi, or 3G/4G Internet connection and a DIRECTV Plus\xc2\xae DVR or HD DVR. Receivers do not require phone or Internet connection to schedule a recording.- On Demand scheduling requires a DIRECTV Plus\xc2\xae HD DVR (model HR20 or later or R22) connected to the Internet.- Tips, Tricks and Customer Support are available on the DIRECTV websiteUse of the DIRECTV iPhone Application by DIRECTV customers is subject to DIRECTV's Customer Agreement and Privacy Policy (available on the DIRECTV website).Recent changes:NEW IN THIS VERSION- Live TV streaming inside and outside of your home network for select channels, including AUDIENCE Network \xe2\x84\xa2.- Closed Captioning support for DIRECTV Everywhere & Live TV streaming- Enhanced Search functionality to show results as you type, top picks of the week, and listings of programs that you can watch on your Android phone.- Support links"
